#~ " data is wiped. If OEM Unlocking "
#~ "is disabled, someone can still boot "
#~ "up in recovery mode, enter the "
#~ "menu, wipe data, then boot the OS"
#~ " and enable OEM unlocking. Therefore "
#~ "it doesn't really increase the security"
#~ " but `disabling it <index.html>`_ reduces"
#~ " the potential physical attack surface."
